I learned plenty from the course and plan on completing Powerpoint to complete the three part series.  The final week is an honors assignment. I completed the assignment in Excel and now this one in Word. The honors assignments are very good assignments to check your understanding of what is taught during the course. But, the submission process is too complicated. Because of this, I spent so much time trying to find a fellow student that submitted the assignment the proper way that would allow me to complete the peer review. I finally gave up for today and I will try again tomorrow. I noticed this issue with Excel as well. I am completely sure that we students are the ones responsible for not properly completing the submission of the honors assignment, but never the less it's not a good process if it ends in failure.

- comparing documents, track changes
